<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM5.4.10">
<l>alli māta ramarun tirumār vaṉaraṅkattai</l>
<l>kalliṉ maṉṉu matiḷmaṅ kaiyarkōṉ kalikaṉṟicol</l>
<l>nalli caimā laikaḷnā liraṇṭu miraṇṭumuṭaṉ</l>
<l>valla vartā mulakāṇ ṭupiṉvā ṉulakāḷvarē.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Those who master these four-[times]-two-plus-two [verses] altogether,</l>
<l rend="indent">this fine musical garland,</l>
<l>The words of Kaliyaṉ, king of those of Maṅkai, with sturdy walls of stone,</l>
<l>About Araṅkam of the one on whose divine chest rests the lady of the lotus,</l>
<l>Having ruled this world, they will later rule the world of heaven.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
